title: Delirio Tropical
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Buffet, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Dishes on rotation throughout the week include salads and hot items. At least 4 or 5 of the salads are vegan and are clearly labeled. At least one hot item is vegan including a veggie burger pattie, veggie meatballs or falafel. Offers a selection of desserts, coffee and drinks. Air conditioned comfy place.
